{"tid":2205110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【白羅老豆搵仔】白羅斯示威　300 警員資料被公開","createTime":"2020-09-16T14:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T15:09:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3db053fde675f75dd5273fcee571b0dbaef09175","tid":2205110,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T14:23:15.000Z","msg":"自去年反送中運動以來，有香港網民披露大量警員個人資料，律政司和警方去年 10 月獲法庭批出臨時禁制令，禁止這些「起底」行為。近日的白羅斯示威活動亦出現警員被「起底」的情況，當地警方周三（16 日）表示，有 300 名警員的個人資料被外洩上網。<br />\n<br />\n執政近 26 年的白羅斯總統盧卡申科被指在 8 月 9 日的大選涉嫌舞弊，當地爆發的大規模反政府示威持續至今，過程中多次出現防暴警員暴力對待示威者的場面，亦有示威者試圖出手扯開防暴警員的面罩。<br />\n<br />\n當地內政部高級安全官員 Andrei Parshin 在周三表示，有 300 名警員的個人資料外洩被放上網，「超過 250 名警員及其家人受到壓力」。當局針對涉嫌威嚇警員的人士開展了 43 宗刑事案件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%80%81%E8%B1%86%E6%90%B5%E4%BB%94-%E7%99%BD%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-300-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%25B1%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-300-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=cc6955f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E8%25B1%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E4%25BB%2594-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-300-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%2F&h=da46b7de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%80%81%E8%B1%86%E6%90%B5%E4%BB%94-%E7%99%BD%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-300-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"87407dbdf68b0e70f9253d2a1419d3c62ed